        "setup": "Get your client certificate from the [Teller Dashboard Certificates page](https://teller.io/settings/certificates). Teller creates a certificate and private key when you sign up; if you no longer have `teller.zip`, revoke the old certificate and issue a new one from that dashboard page. Use the resulting `cert.pem` and private key for mTLS requests to `https://api.teller.io/`.",
